content: I'm getting Duplicate element id "X" errors on the snapshot for every element of a StructureDefinition (but this is only happening on 1 profile in the IG), which I don't understand because the element id's are duplicated across the differential and snapshot, by definition, right? I'm sure I'm doing something wrong, but I can't figure out what it is. Anyone seen this?

It is duplicating slice definitions, and I've verified that it's happening with the latest publisher and that the source differential only has 1. What I have is a case where I have a common nested slice name across slices. I'll try renaming the nested slices uniquely.
The snapshot processor does strange things when you mix up slice names and id's :)
